title: Rachel & Becca Review Clare’s Men!
description:
It’s the podcast you’ve been waiting for! Rachel and Becca review the photos and bios of all 31 men competing for Clare’s heart on this season of “The Bachelorette.” 

Plus, Hannah Ann Sluss stops by to discuss her new podcast with Tayshia and Joe: “Click Bait with Bachelor Nation.” 

Be sure to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
